Class SimulatedInstrumentModule

java.lang.Object
  abstractModulePack.AbstractDeviceModule
      abstractModulePack.AbstractInstrumentModule
          simulatorPack.SimulatedInstrumentModule
All Implemented Interfaces:
DeviceInterface, MeasurementInstrumentInterface, ModuleListener
public class SimulatedInstrumentModule
extends AbstractInstrumentModule

This is a simulated measurement instrument that: 1. Can be connected to a signal generator module (can be either a real or a simulated signal generator module). 2. Measures the RMS of the data coming in.
